<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.4.10">
<l>immai yiṭarkkeṭa vēṇṭi yōnteḻil tōḷka likaṉṟi</l>
<l>cemmaip paṉuvaṉūl koṇṭu ceṅkaṇe ṭiyavaṉ ṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>yammamu ṇeṉṟuraik kiṉṟa pāṭali vaiyaintu maintum</l>
<l>meymmai maṉattuvait tētta viṉava rāka lumāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Wishing to end sorrows in this life, when [anyone] praises [the lord],</l>
<l rend="indent">keeping in their hearts,</l>
<l>The truth of these five-and-five songs which say, “Suckle milk,”</l>
<l rend="indent">to the bright-eyed, tall one,</l>
<l>Having learned the elegant literary texts of Kalikaṉṟi,</l>
<l>With sturdy, shapely shoulders, [their] becoming celestials will be certain.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
